org.onyxplatform.api.java

Class TaskScheduler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.onyxplatform.api.java.TaskScheduler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OnyxNames

    public class TaskScheduler
extends java.lang.Object
implements OnyxNames
    The purpose of the task scheduler is to control the order in which available peers are allocated to which tasks. There are a few different Task Scheduler implementations to choose from. The user should consult with the Onyx information model for options.
